		<title>CM9 Code Freeze Has Started</title>
		<link>http://www.cyanogenmod.org/blog/cm9-code-freeze-has-started</link>
		<comments>http://www.cyanogenmod.org/blog/cm9-code-freeze-has-started#comments</comments>
